  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/adde1ee08559cc56301f005b70cdfa75.webp?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash your Animal Instincts!!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/7fd592a5e723714a6e2d05fb4a6b0bfc.poster.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/7fd592a5e723714a6e2d05fb4a6b0bfc.webm?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/7fd592a5e723714a6e2d05fb4a6b0bfc.mp4?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Faunamorph</strong></i> is a 2D metroidvania set in an abandoned underground lab, where you can recombine your own DNA to transform parts of your body into animals limbs. Use the brute strength of a rhino’s horn to break walls, glide over pits with bird wings, and dig tunnels on the ground with mole claws to travel through the laboratory and uncover it’s dark secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/eebdf77b57663315312a7d19b522d483.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/18e65b837b7768c59fd1458e79568935.webp?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shape-Shifting Mastery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/0061d6e7d78054a8dd8da472541731bc.poster.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/0061d6e7d78054a8dd8da472541731bc.webm?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/0061d6e7d78054a8dd8da472541731bc.mp4?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness the power of animal genetics as you transform your body into incredible animal forms, acquiring new abilities to overcome obstacles and uncover the truth. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/228439e3c367e3672e6f961496a6fa35.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Change your DNA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/3ca02309b9e126a26cd479a82268cf1d.poster.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/3ca02309b9e126a26cd479a82268cf1d.webm?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/3ca02309b9e126a26cd479a82268cf1d.mp4?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt on the fly by equipping and swapping abilities, strategically selecting your arsenal of animal powers to suit each challenge and unlock new paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/d0728fc7a0a8e186b6823f75dd0d44f1.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover your Origins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/00615c332fae6fe4030891135d92ed29.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an immersive journey through the dark corridors and hidden chambers of the abandoned lab, piecing together the puzzle of Project H.A.G.E.N's mysterious experiments and your own forgotten past.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/92f4b1f776d71ab3975f2d7e6dec00be.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/9d5332bc994427f3bc83fd715dce299a.webp?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=61 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master your Helix Space by recombining your DNA, switching out your animal abilities on the fly for different combat and exploration scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your body with unique animal abilities, from rolling like an armadillo to swimming like a dolphin, each tailored to overcome new challenges and explore deeper into the lab.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against twisted hulking hybrids, failed experiments and self-defense systems, while testing your skills and powers in creative, intense encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover lore-rich data logs scattered throughout the abandoned lab, revealing the purpose of Project H.A.G.E.N. and the origins of the terrifying hybrid creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a dynamic soundtrack that adapts to your journey, with moods shifting from intense combat to ominous exploration and frenetic survival in near-death moments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a sprawling, interconnected world with rooms to discover and hidden upgrades, adding replayability as you uncover every corner of the lab.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/adde1ee08559cc56301f005b70cdfa75.webp?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unleash your Animal Instincts!!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/7fd592a5e723714a6e2d05fb4a6b0bfc.poster.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/7fd592a5e723714a6e2d05fb4a6b0bfc.webm?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/7fd592a5e723714a6e2d05fb4a6b0bfc.mp4?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Faunamorph</strong></i> is a 2D metroidvania set in an abandoned underground lab, where you can recombine your own DNA to transform parts of your body into animals limbs. Use the brute strength of a rhino’s horn to break walls, glide over pits with bird wings, and dig tunnels on the ground with mole claws to travel through the laboratory and uncover it’s dark secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/eebdf77b57663315312a7d19b522d483.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/18e65b837b7768c59fd1458e79568935.webp?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shape-Shifting Mastery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/0061d6e7d78054a8dd8da472541731bc.poster.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/0061d6e7d78054a8dd8da472541731bc.webm?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/0061d6e7d78054a8dd8da472541731bc.mp4?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness the power of animal genetics as you transform your body into incredible animal forms, acquiring new abilities to overcome obstacles and uncover the truth. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/228439e3c367e3672e6f961496a6fa35.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Change your DNA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/3ca02309b9e126a26cd479a82268cf1d.poster.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/3ca02309b9e126a26cd479a82268cf1d.webm?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/3ca02309b9e126a26cd479a82268cf1d.mp4?t=1773857811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt on the fly by equipping and swapping abilities, strategically selecting your arsenal of animal powers to suit each challenge and unlock new paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/d0728fc7a0a8e186b6823f75dd0d44f1.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Uncover your Origins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/00615c332fae6fe4030891135d92ed29.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an immersive journey through the dark corridors and hidden chambers of the abandoned lab, piecing together the puzzle of Project H.A.G.E.N's mysterious experiments and your own forgotten past.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/92f4b1f776d71ab3975f2d7e6dec00be.avif?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/9d5332bc994427f3bc83fd715dce299a.webp?t=1773857811\" width=616 height=61 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master your Helix Space by recombining your DNA, switching out your animal abilities on the fly for different combat and exploration scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your body with unique animal abilities, from rolling like an armadillo to swimming like a dolphin, each tailored to overcome new challenges and explore deeper into the lab.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against twisted hulking hybrids, failed experiments and self-defense systems, while testing your skills and powers in creative, intense encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover lore-rich data logs scattered throughout the abandoned lab, revealing the purpose of Project H.A.G.E.N. and the origins of the terrifying hybrid creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a dynamic soundtrack that adapts to your journey, with moods shifting from intense combat to ominous exploration and frenetic survival in near-death moments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a sprawling, interconnected world with rooms to discover and hidden upgrades, adding replayability as you uncover every corner of the lab.</p></li></ul>",
